snippet: The protests that began on Wall Street have struck a chord, and on Monday a coalition of Chicago groups will demonstrate outside meetings held by the Mortgage Bankers and Futures Industry Associations.
lead_paragraph: The protests that began on Wall Street have struck a chord, and on Monday a coalition of Chicago groups will demonstrate outside meetings held by the Mortgage Bankers and Futures Industry Associations.
